deck: Agent of SHIELD.
description:
Origin

An agent of SHIELD.

Creation

Written by Scott Lobdell and drawn by Joe Madureira.

Story Arcs

In the Phalanx Covenant, Agent Santora is on duty at a SHIELD safe house in California and grows tired of the tedium of standing watch. Her boredom is alleviated, however, when it is noted that puddles of water are forming where no person is standing. Agent Santora joins other agents in confronting Banshee and Emma Frost (who had been psionically hiding their presence). No arrest can be made, however, once Banshee lets out a scream. The agents are simply left with a ringing headache.
